Adebimpe Oyebade (amụrụ na Machị 23, 1997) nke a maara nke ọma dị ka Mo Bimpe bụ onye Naijirịa na-eme ihe nkiri nke a maara maka mmeri 2018 City People Entertainment Awards maka Best New Actress of the Year.
A mụrụ Oyebade Adebimpe na Machị 23, 1997 ma bụrụ nwa afọ Ijero na Ekiti Steetị.
Adebimpe lụrụ Lateef Adedimeji na Disemba 2021.
